title: Emilie De Ravin pregnant
text:
Updated: 12:58 pm 
Actress Emilie De Ravin is expecting her first child. 
The Australian, who stars in U.S. TV drama "Once Upon a Time," is pregnant by her boyfriend, Eric Bilitch. 
She announced the happy news on Friday, taking to Twitter.com to write, "I wanted to share some exciting news... me & @ericbilitch are expecting a baby!! 'Tis truly a dream come true and we could not be happier." 
Bilitch then retweeted the message and added, "Indeed! We are over the moon with joy! Could not be more excited to be starting a family with Emilie." 
De Ravin and director/writer Bilitch got together last year after her divorce from Joshua Janowicz. They married in 2006 but split up several times before eventually making the break-up official in 2013. Copyright WENN.com
